oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Clinch Avenue
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Thompson Brothers
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Clinch Avenue at Market Street, Knoxville, TN. Draughon's Business College at right, traffic tower, streetcar, Fouche Block Building at right, Custom House and Todd & Armistead Drugstore. Signs for Coca-Cola, J.N. Janeway, Chiropractic Heath Service, and Roth Coal. Bicycles parked on street. Damaged.
